@end{Syntax}

@begin{Legality}
The renamed entity shall be a generic unit of the corresponding kind.
@end{Legality}

@begin{StaticSem}
A @nt{generic_renaming_declaration} declares a new view
@Redundant{of the renamed generic unit}.
